///|
/// MoonKit - A comprehensive utility toolkit for MoonBit.
///
/// Provides TOML data types, semantic versioning, ULID generation,
/// string case conversion, and common data validators.
///
/// ## Packages
///
/// - `toml` - TOML v1.0 data types and document manipulation
/// - `semver` - Semantic Versioning 2.0.0 parser and comparator
/// - `ulid` - ULID unique identifier generation
/// - `strcase` - String case conversion (camelCase, snake_case, etc.)
/// - `validators` - Data validation functions (email, URL, etc.)
